$ Oracle: Init parameter _OPTIMIZER_COST_BASED_TRANSFORMATION
@ _optimizer_cost_based_transformation

The value of `_optimizer_cost_based_transformation` specifies the amount of work performed by the → development/databases/Oracle/optimizer#qry-optimizer-qry-tran[optimizer query transformer].

The value of `_optimizer_cost_based_transformation` can be set to
table { ll
  `on` ☰
  `off` ☰
  `exhaustive` ☰
  `iterative` ☰
  `linear` ☰
table }

The default value of `_optimizer_cost_based_transformation` is dependent on the value of `→ development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters/optimizer/features_enable`.

sa:

  The → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters
